CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 25, 1959, pg. 13 reads: "Tax Lien Transcribing - Front to rear: Rose Levin, utility clerk; Ollie Brown, typist; Frank Mansfield, general supervisor, and Butah Strickland, special utility clerk."
TitMainTitle: Rose Levin, Ollie Brown, and Butah Strickland, examining documents and ledgers, with Frank Mansfield, standing behind them, in Allegheny County Prothonotary Office
